Source: mythplugins
Section: graphics
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Matt Zimmerman <mdz@debian.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>> 3.0.0), libmyth-0.19-dev, kdelibs4-dev, xlibmesa-gl-dev | xlibmesa-dev | libgl-dev, libdvdread3-dev, libvorbis-dev (>= 1.0.0-1), libflac-dev (>= 1.0.4-4), libmad0-dev, libcdaudio0-dev, libcdparanoia0-dev, libid3tag0-dev, fftw-dev, libsdl1.2-dev, liblame-dev, libfaad2-dev, g++-3.3, libexif-dev (>= 0.6.9-6), libtiff4-dev | libtiff-dev
Standards-Version: 3.5.2
Bugs: mailto:mdz@debian.org

Package: mythplugins
Architecture: all
Recommends: mythweb, mythbrowser, mythdvd, mythmusic, mythnews, mythvideo, mythweather
Description: Wrapper package for MythTV plugins.

Package: mythbrowser
Architecture: any
Depends: mythtv-common (>= 0.11-2), mythtv-frontend (>= 0.19-1), ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: A small web browser module for MythTV

Package: mythdvd
Architecture: any
Depends: mythtv-common (>= 0.11-2), mythtv-frontend (>= 0.19-1), ${shlibs:Depends}
Recommends: xine | ogle | mplayer
Suggests: transcode, mythvideo
Description: DVD add-on module for MythTV
 MythDVD provides an interface for launching your preferred DVD player
 from MythTV, and also supports transcoding DVDs into audio/video
 streams which can be played by MythVideo, using the transcode package.

Package: mythgallery
Architecture: all
Depends: mythtv-common (>= 0.11-2), mythtv-frontend (>= 0.19-1), ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Image gallery/slideshow add-on module for MythTV
 MythGallery allows you to visually browse a directory tree containing
 image files.  It can display any image file format supported by Qt,
 and supports image rotation and simple slideshows.

Package: mythmusic
Architecture: any
Depends: mythtv-common (>= 0.11-2), mythtv-frontend (>= 0.19-1), ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Music add-on module for MythTV
 MythMusic provides a digital audio jukebox integrated with MythTV.
 It supports Ogg Vorbis, FLAC and MP3 streams, displays
 visualizations, and can also encode new Ogg Vorbis or FLAC streams
 from audio CDs using a CD-ROM drive.

Package: mythnews
Architecture: any
Depends: mythtv-common (>= 0.11-2), mythtv-frontend (>= 0.19-1), ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: An RSS feed news reader module for MythTV

Package: mythvideo
Architecture: any
Depends: mythtv-common (>= 0.11-2), mythtv-frontend (>= 0.19-1), ${shlibs:Depends}, libxml-simple-perl, libwww-perl
Description: A generic video player frontend module for MythTV
 MythVideo allows you to browse and play video streams, using an external
 player, from within the MythTV interface.

Package: mythweather
Architecture: any
Depends: mythtv-common, mythtv-frontend (>= 0.19-1), ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Weather add-on module for MythTV
 MythWeather displays current and forecast weather information within
 MythTV.

Package: mythweb
Architecture: all
Depends: mythtv-common, apache2 | httpd, libapache2-mod-php4 | php4, php4-mysql
Description: Web interface add-on module for MythTV
 MythWeb provides a web interface which can be used to view listings,
 schedule recordings, delete recordings, and search for programs.
 It can also browse mythmusic's music database, and may eventually
 support playing music streams as well.
